                    <li>Barangay Clearance/Barangay Certificate and Barangay Indigency (1 original) </li>
                    <li>Any VAlid ID of the client (much better if they have ID addressed to their province) (bring original and 1 photocopy)</li>
                    <li>Police blotter (victim of illegal recruitment, victims of pick pockets, strandees during typoon (1 original)</li>
                    <li>Personal Letter of Request for Burial/Funeral Assistance Addressed to Mayor.</li>
                    <li>General Intake Sheet (CSWDO Form) and Certificate of Eligibility (1 original)</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <a href="/transportation-assistance/form">
                <button class="btn btn-primary">Proceed</button>
            </a>
